equation: 0.372 * smooth(1, if mech_car.vehicle.fDrag.v >= 0.0 then mech_car.vehicle.fDrag.v ^ 2.0 else -mech_car.vehicle.fDrag.v ^ 2.0)
lead_car.continuousClock1.offset + (if time < lead_car.continuousClock1.startTime then 0.0 else time - lead_car.continuousClock1.startTime)
lead_car.add3.k1 * lead_car.product.y + lead_car.add3.k2 * lead_car.x_l0.k + lead_car.add3.k3 * lead_car.integrator1.y
pID_controller.add3.k1 * pID_controller.gain.y + pID_controller.add3.k2 * pID_controller.integrator.y + pID_controller.add3.k3 * pID_controller.derivative.y
